      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels so heavy. like i am just taking up space. i spend all day staring at a screen and talking to people via text, but i wonder if anyone would even notice if i just... stopped. like if i just stopped appearing online or in real life entirely. would it even leave a dent?",
